	<element name="Grudgeglass Crystal" type="Item" source="Pirates" id="ID_PIRATES_ITEM_GRUDGEGLASS_CRYSTAL">
		<description>
			<p>Appearance: Deep red glass with dark veins—some like ink stains, others like cracks.</p>
			<p>Function: Magical barriers, wards, and alarms</p>
			<p>Power Source: Anchored to unresolved grudges sealed into contracts or blood-oaths</p>
			<p>Quirk: Cracks and shatters when a connected soul breaks a bargain or oath</p>
			<p>Hidden Effect: Weapons: Can be bound to a person’s name to act as a long-range tether for tracking. (huntersmark) shield spell for armour. </p>
			<p>Special feature on the counter: The crystals pulsate slightly when a customer who has ever broken a vow stands in front of them. When a promise is broken, they crack audibly. </p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="keywords">soul crystal</set>
			<set name="category">Treasure</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">5</set>
			<set name="stackable">true</set>
			<set name="valuable">true</set>
			<set name="rarity">Rare</set>
		</setters>
	</element>
